maxiofs (0.9.1-beta) unstable; urgency=high

  * Release v0.9.1-beta - Security: tenant isolation hardening
  * Fixed 12 tenant isolation vulnerabilities across console API handlers
  * IDP handlers: tenant admins restricted to own tenant IDPs only
