  * Access key handlers: list/create/delete now verify target user tenant ownership
  * Bucket permission handlers: list/grant/revoke now require admin + bucket ownership
  * handleDeleteBucket, handleListBucketShares, handleDeleteShare: queryTenantID restricted to global admins
  * handleGetTenant, handleListTenantUsers: tenant admins restricted to own tenant
  * Frontend: IDP tenant selector for global admins, tenant name resolution in IDP list

