  * Major feature release: Bucket Replication, Advanced Logging & Test Coverage
  * Bucket Replication System - S3-compatible cross-bucket replication
  * Support for AWS S3, MinIO, and other MaxIOFS instances as destinations
  * Three replication modes: Realtime, Scheduled (interval-based), Batch (manual)
